data.name: ABOUT
data.value:
GUI4CBM4WIN by Leif Bloomquist (no support anymore) & adoption to OpenCBM 0.4.0 by Wolfgang (http://d81.de/)
This is a simple GUI front-end for OpenCBM by Spiro Trikaliotis (www.trikaliotis.net/cbm4win/)
OpenCBM itself is heavily based on cbm4linux written by Michael Klein (http://www.lb.shuttle.de/puffin/)
This is version {0} of the GUI, which is currently maintained by Payton Byrd (payton@paytonbyrd.com) and is distributed under the BSD OpenSource license.
